{"tid":344750,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[飲茶]有無人鐘意飲冷泡茶","createTime":"2017-08-02T13:14:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-31T11:49:01.000Z","uid":33359,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f5ada456530e2f368f669416e3c8d75378024618","tid":344750,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T13:14:48.000Z","msg":"自製冷泡茶，其實超乎想像的便宜又簡單，有幾個主要優點：<br />\n<br />\n〔天然香甜，不苦不澀〕冷泡利用長時間讓茶的甘甜成分緩慢釋出，不容易有苦澀味，能更明顯地感受到茶的天然甘甜。<br />\n<br />\n〔低咖啡因，不刺激〕相較於咖啡甚至是熱泡的茶，冷泡釋出的咖啡因含量更低，即使對咖啡因較敏感的人也可以安心享用。<br />\n<br />\n〔容易製作，低門檻〕工具簡單，只要一個空瓶和冷水，無需繁瑣複雜的步驟，只要掌握冷泡茶比例，人人都可以輕鬆泡出清涼可口的冷泡茶，別再依賴市售的化學調味茶囉。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://wolftea.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/DSC1554-1024x683.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwolftea.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2FDSC1554-1024x683.jpg&h=9a589ab3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n除左普洱之外大部份茶葉都可以咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d6be5342d38022b5c3e2fcd00eeaf43097506bb","tid":344750,"uid":62969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T13:18:36.000Z","msg":"認真冇咁香"},{"pid":"b4c89c438fcaaf32f5f0d722d80b7b874e4fca33","tid":344750,"uid":18667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T13:19:30.000Z","msg":"識飲一定飲凍頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c745f0e6d0d8ea05aee6c771eb098faa8e0e668","tid":344750,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T13:19:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認真冇咁香</blockquote><br />\n香味一定係差D<br />\n但係唔會訓唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又唔會苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da0caa25fedc3a1229ad86ad7d186130e255eb07","tid":344750,"uid":106326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T13:21:00.000Z","msg":"有冇試過邊種茶出既效果會好啲？<br />\n用開咩水？"},{"pid":"4c4cc4b22b4121b2fb9491b563944d6710547e30","tid":344750,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T13:21:42.000Z","msg":"花茶呢？"},{"pid":"7cc62b02927f436426dc40cd52d5c198f3f3f4e8","tid":344750,"uid":33359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T13:23:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇試過邊種茶出既效果會好啲？<br />\n用開咩水？</blockquote><br />\n我試過用茶葉,茶包<br />\n兩者差唔多<br />\n<br />\n茶葉用大紅袍,唔錯,幾好飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n茶包用過GRAY TEA,好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d940caa3ac526cd11f907dce4bb364c864fb7095","tid":344750,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T13:26:47.000Z","msg":"有一試既價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"171c03253d660db7bd63db7ac099a9a6d45303a2","tid":344750,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T13:29:59.000Z","msg":"有冇話啲水要幾凍 ?<br />\n<br />\n飲水機 嗰啲 ?  泡幾耐 ?<br />\n<br />\n定係 普通溫水都得 ?"},{"pid":"5a88b8c882e56e41d7383adcea06e96bd13234b0","tid":344750,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T13:38:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇話啲水要幾凍 ?<br />\n<br />\n飲水機 嗰啲 ?  泡幾耐 ?<br />\n<br />\n定係 普通溫水都得 ?</blockquote><br />\n凍水,唔同茶葉泡既時間唔一樣<br />\n但唔好超過十個鐘"},{"pid":"b02060ea92d5d75d65d7170599e0e2430942f2e3","tid":344750,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T13:51:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有一試既價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n訓前沖定一樽,第朝有得飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"100fd79caf23f012f3eb1c06f0376c6a5ec4cb7e","tid":344750,"uid":44339,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T14:02:57.000Z","msg":"幾年前，台灣買茶葉，老闆教過我<br />\n堅係正，但唔旅雪櫃，放室溫得唔得？"},{"pid":"49424cbd839fb4f434e63343f55ac61ccd23d765","tid":344750,"uid":33359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T14:08:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾年前，台灣買茶葉，老闆教過我<br />\n堅係正，但唔旅雪櫃，放室溫得唔得？</blockquote><br />\n唔熱就得"},{"pid":"998ce272fd48629ed9dd9c02c9034fc8cda4d593","tid":344750,"uid":110699,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T14:08:49.000Z","msg":"大紅袍，鐵觀音<br />\n<br />\n冷泡唔係飲香<br />\n係飲茶嘅滑<br />\n同埋飲得爽好多"},{"pid":"a7c257c4f3e2839055ce5965f7872d86ec45d51b","tid":344750,"uid":110699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T14:09:32.000Z","msg":"仲有甘味"},{"pid":"86ebe48ead7a2ffc0d1d6151d59c5f3de7d76a70","tid":344750,"uid":33359,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T14:11:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大紅袍，鐵觀音<br />\n<br />\n冷泡唔係飲香<br />\n係飲茶嘅滑<br />\n同埋飲得爽好多</blockquote><br />\n仲有甘甜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67f6a027a5a97d9211724f5384dbabc29be7bfa2","tid":344750,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T14:28:48.000Z","msg":"幾乎所有的茶都可以做冷泡茶<br />\n冷泡茶適合的茶種：<br />\n東方美人、紅茶、綠茶、熟茶、包種茶、碧螺春。<br />\n也有研究報告指出：高山茶所泡的冷泡茶，對於降低血壓與降低尿酸具有特別的功效。<br />\n冷泡茶沖泡時間：4~8小時。<br />\n以我個人比較喜歡5小時，以下茶味未完全釋出、以上會有些澀味，<br />\n冷泡茶沖泡比例：茶葉與水=1克：100毫升<br />\n大家可依自己喜好調整時間和濃淡。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"408cacc149552e06d0bd8410dccceeeb103443e3","tid":344750,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T14:36:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾乎所有的茶都可以做冷泡茶<br />\n冷泡茶適合的茶種：<br />\n東方美人、紅茶、綠茶、熟茶、包種茶、碧螺春。<br />\n也有研究報告指出：高山茶所泡的冷泡茶，對於降低血壓與降低尿酸具有特別的功效。<br />\n冷泡茶沖泡時間：4~8小時。<br />\n以我個人比較喜歡5小時，以下茶味未完全釋出、以上會有些澀味，<br />\n冷泡茶沖泡比例：茶葉與水=1克：100毫升<br />\n大家可依自己喜好調整時間和濃淡。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原來要 浸咁耐架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98de1f14f60215d702b2f72d2d7e70f92bfda9c0","tid":344750,"uid":10292,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T14:37:21.000Z","msg":"試下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03a4e62ed41ff7a29be548507eed111a920b3745","tid":344750,"uid":47819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T14:38:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港邊度買靚茶葉好"},{"pid":"f35399f06e9efadb78cfd016b2511e6de4c752d5","tid":344750,"uid":2327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T14:42:34.000Z","msg":"成日飲剩d茶連茶葉放雪櫃 <br />\n第朝起身 好飲到仆街 不過唔知浸咁耐有無害"},{"pid":"6af0749c4fe05acfd47d79821285f55a77ec37b4","tid":344750,"uid":47819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T14:43:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成日飲剩d茶連茶葉放雪櫃 <br />\n第朝起身 好飲到仆街 不過唔知浸咁耐有無害</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實唔好覺得好澀咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d22e43c9a87c880a71afee62ed6146b491541f41","tid":344750,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T14:43:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成日飲剩d茶連茶葉放雪櫃 <br />\n第朝起身 好飲到仆街 不過唔知浸咁耐有無害</blockquote><br />\n盡量唔超過十個鐘就無乜問題"},{"pid":"66459cf46934aa5a564976d0dbbf273ea9ac45bc","tid":344750,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T14:46:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/02/224604_bd33ecf49496f1362e829160c566c8c7.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F02%2F224604_bd33ecf49496f1362e829160c566c8c7.JPG&h=37ff0c9b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"56686da42e62c6f41916aa73108f9f47e7f7a65b","tid":344750,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T14:59:53.000Z","msg":"今晚沖呢個<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/02/225943_21afcd7fae4385839a91656539d0f446.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?