8-04T11:20:31.000Z","msg":"今日行759 就見錫蘭黑綠茶有得賣<br />\n7折後 $10.9<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/6ax1frj2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F6ax1frj2&h=2f2c541a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b8dd24bf7bdee00b265ead1341fd1bac921788cb","tid":344750,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T11:32:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今日行759 就見錫蘭黑綠茶有得賣<br />\n7折後 $10.9<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/6ax1frj2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F6ax1frj2&h=2f2c541a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n白色個盒咩味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我個間無既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b3416cc7792de255d591b910b6f677fea72b140","tid":344750,"uid":75993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T11:35:16.000Z","msg":"點解普洱唔得嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91e5fdfe16c00857cca571842a0ff8b13363abae","tid":344750,"uid":68412,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T11:47:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>[quote]今日行759 就見錫蘭黑綠茶有得賣<br />\n7折後 $10.9<br />\n<br />\n白色個盒咩味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我個間無既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好似係咩奶茶，所以無買<br />\n<br />\n上網查見台灣網寫 --- 牛奶烏龍綠茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce48d751ebc80224b1e36a05c23edace604ffa89","tid":344750,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T11:48:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解普洱唔得嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一般來說，茶葉發酵時間越久，茶葉含磷就越高。而冷泡茶需要含磷比較低的茶葉，也就是要選擇發酵程度低或者無發酵的茶。也就是說，發酵程度較低的茶葉，冷泡起來口感更為芬芳甘美。綠茶、發酵較輕的烏龍茶、白茶中的白豪銀針和白牡丹都比較適合冷泡；發酵程度較高的紅茶、鐵觀音、普洱茶則不適合冷泡，即使泡出來也是味道苦澀、無香氣。<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://read01.com/RAne3M.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fread01.com%2FRAne3M.html&d=u%2F1HYRBVLHCuqs5ou2zj7G6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=6f0eee9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://read01.com/RAne3M.html</a>"},{"pid":"fcd661962f8fba0fc3071f566023c460791c8fde","tid":344750,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T11:48:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>[quote]今日行759 就見錫蘭黑綠茶有得賣<br />\n7折後 $10.9<br />\n<br />\n白色個盒咩味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我個間無既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好似係咩奶茶，所以無買<br />\n<br />\n上網查見台灣網寫 --- 牛奶烏龍綠茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n聽落好似幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0787a2bfd8e8b9634c75166d84e292b9364d6567","tid":344750,"uid":68412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T11:50:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 港島撚表示搵唔到！！！<br />\n(官塘邊間?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係電氣道148號分店買"},{"pid":"f7725d7e61a0953019e7effb156418904599d4f6","tid":344750,"uid":103718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T12:07:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解普洱唔得嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一般來說，茶葉發酵時間越久，茶葉含磷就越高。而冷泡茶需要含磷比較低的茶葉，也就是要選擇發酵程度低或者無發酵的茶。也就是說，發酵程度較低的茶葉，冷泡起來口感更為芬芳甘美。綠茶、發酵較輕的烏龍茶、白茶中的白豪銀針和白牡丹都比較適合冷泡；發酵程度較高的紅茶、鐵觀音、普洱茶則不適合冷泡，即使泡出來也是味道苦澀、無香氣。<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://read01.com/RAne3M.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fread01.com%2FRAne3M.html&d=u%2F1HYRBVLHCuqs5ou2zj7G6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=6f0eee9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://read01.com/RAne3M.html</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n正解。 <br />\n<br />\n而且普洱同紅茶用冷泡真係唔會比熱泡好飲。 加上普洱同紅茶冇咁多咖啡因亦唔太苦，冇乜需要冷泡。<br />\n<br />\n烏龍係要有回甘先好，用黎沖冷泡好似有少少浪費。<br />\n<br />\n所以我覺得冷泡比較上岩用綠茶、清香型烏龍及白茶"},{"pid":"41f853fdca5c64032db4ce4ba37c9e51807e1548","tid":344750,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T01:04:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87ca8190460d6740162188478dd26a30690f4c5f","tid":344750,"uid":69985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T01:13:32.000Z","msg":"請問用twining 既earl grey茶包 得唔得?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"043fa94d6b17724fdf80b57e630ac7e3ad70e57e","tid":344750,"uid":59041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T01:20:03.000Z","msg":"有飲開茶，早一兩年係台灣試過冷泡茶覺得幾好飲，<br />\n不過擔心個問題，茶葉一般唔建議泡既時間長，<br />\n驚重金屬同殘留多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d278d94b190655ea489c89625d58f67ec61eef26","tid":344750,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T01:55:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>請問用twining 既earl grey茶包 得唔得?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我試過用GREY TEA,唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"556fb72b29480c8a973f806259c530066b332be8","tid":344750,"uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T02:55:35.000Z","msg":"成個櫃都係<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/05/105531_8ea40e70dd01d0f511dd698f60969c81.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F05%2F105531_8ea40e70dd01d0f511dd698f60969c81.jpg&h=d3dd1f63&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3822969165c287e3a0c99750096b9a6bd2b4a085","tid":344750,"uid":37204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T03:00:19.000Z","msg":"<